# Claude Model Version Rule

**IMPORTANT**: Always use the latest Claude 4.5 model versions in all code, examples, and documentation.

## Required Model Names

Use these model identifiers exclusively:

- ✅ `claude-haiku-4-5` - Fastest model (replaces claude-3-haiku-20240307)
- ✅ `claude-sonnet-4-5` - Balanced model (replaces claude-3-sonnet-*, claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022)
- ✅ `claude-opus-4-5` - Most capable model (replaces claude-3-opus-*)

