## Examples

### Configuration
```php
$config = new AgentConfig(
    model: 'claude-sonnet-4-5',  // ✅ Correct
    maxTokens: 1024
);
```

### Client Initialization
```php
$client = new ClaudeClient(
    apiKey: $apiKey,
    model: 'claude-haiku-4-5'  // ✅ Correct - fast model
);
```

### Documentation Examples
```php
// ✅ Always use current model names in tutorials
$tracing->startTrace($id, 'operation', [
